DRAAD-176A: Node Version Fix Deployment
===========================================
Timestamp: 2025-12-14T14:47:00Z

ROOT CAUSE:
- Railway Railpack kon Node 20.18.0 NIET lokaliseren
- Log error: "Failed to resolve version 20.18.0 of node"

FIXES APPLIED:
1. package.json: "node": "20.18.0" → "node": ">=20.0.0"
2. railway.toml: nixpacks = "node-20.18.0" → nixpacks = "node-20"

BENEFITS:
- Flexibel versie-beheer (node-20 is LTS)
- Railpack kan nu beschikbare LTS-versie gebruiken
- Geen hardcoded versie-constraint

STATUS: Ready for deployment via Railway
